maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/791/s.orig: Halfway through! I'll go to the end and wait for you.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/791/s.text: Vous êtes à la moitié du chemin ! Je vais aller vers la fin et vous attendre.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Game Tester
Hey you!
I'm one of the testers for this game!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Je suis un des testeurs de ce jeu !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: The devs asked me to test an almost finished new quest type: \c[3]Parkour\c[0]!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Les développeurs m'ont demandé de tester un nouveau type de quête quasiment terminé : \c[3]Parkour\c[0] !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: I'm kinda tired and you just came along. So\..\..\.. Wanna try it out?
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Je suis assez fatigué et je t'ai vu arriver. Donc\..\..\.. Tu veux essayer ?

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Nice! Good to see some enthusiasm!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Trop cool ! C'est bon de voir de l'enthousiasme !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Alright, get this. You will start right next to me.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: OK, prends ça. Tu vas démarrer juste à côté de moi.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: When you touch this checkpoint, another will pop up.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Quand tu atteindras ce point de contrôle, un autre apparaitra.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Your goal is to walk through every marker until you hit the last one.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Ton but est d'atteindre tous les marqueurs jusqu'à arriver au dernier.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Aaaaand the last one is over there.
It will only appear after you hit the last normal marker.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Il apparaitra seulement après que tu touches le dernier marqueur normal.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Yeah, I know. But it's more fun that way right?
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Oui, je sais. Mais c'est plus marrant comme ça, non ?

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Well, at least if you like running.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Bon, au moins, si tu aimes courir.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Also, if you leave the map all your progress is lost!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Sinon, si tu quittes la carte, toute ta progression sera perdue !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Another bummer, I know.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Oui je sais, c'est assez idiot.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Anyway!
Ready to try?
[nods]
Awesome! As I said, just start by stepping on the first marker here!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Génial ! Comme je le disais, démarre en marchant sur ce premier marqueur ci !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: [shakes head]
Really? Oh man, I don't wanna do this all alone.
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Vraiment ? Oh, je ne vais pas y arriver tout seul. Il nous faudra plus de postes en contrôle qualité.

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: That's like\..\..\.. so much work.
If you ever change your mind...
Come back, alright?\.\.\. Please?
Just one more, it's right next to you!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Encore un, il est juste à côté de toi !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: Go on, you can do it!
The next marker awaits!
[nods]
Just step on this first marker here and start running!
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.text: Marche juste sur ce premier marqueur ci et commence à courir !

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/793/s.orig: [nods]
Just one more, it's right next to you!

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/813/s.orig: And there was no problem, right? No sudden shocks or anything?
maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/813/s.text: Et il n'a eu aucun problème, non ? Pas de bugs soudain ou autre ?

maps/autumn/path-7-1.json/entities/813/s.orig: Thanks a lot! Take this for your efforts.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Christophorus
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Christophorus

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Hi!
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Salut !

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Ah, I see you managed to collect the chest over there.\. Nice work.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Ah, je vois que tu as réussi à ouvrir le coffre là-bas.\. Joli travail.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: At least you're not one of those players that just blindly keep jumping into the water here, trying to make that impossible jump.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Au moins, tu n'es pas un de ces joueurs qui continuent bêtement de sauter dans l'eau en essayant de réussir ce saut impossible.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: I've been at this spot a lot and trust me... I've seen things.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Je viens souvent dans le coin et crois-moi... J'en ai vu des trucs.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Yes, what is it?
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Oui, qu'est-ce qu'il y a ?

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Let me guess. You wonder how to reach this chest, don't you?
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Laisse-moi deviner. Tu te demandes comment on atteint ce coffre, non ?

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Figured...
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Je me demandais aussi...

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Well, you may have realized this already, but jumping from here on those pillars is not the right solution.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Bon, tu l'as peut-être déjà remarqué, mais sauter d'ici sur ces piliers, ce n'est pas la bonne solution.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: No, you'll have to go another way. In fact it's a very round-about path to reach it.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Non, il faut passer par une autre route. En fait, c'est un bon détour qu'il faut faire pour l'atteindre.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Do you want to know more? I suggest you try to find the way yourself. It's more rewarding.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Tu veux en savoir plus ? Je pense qu'il faut que tu trouves le chemin par toi-même. C'est plus gratifiant.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: [nods]
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: [acquiesce]

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Alright then...
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Bon OK...

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: From here go to the \c[3]west\c[0], close to the exit.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: D'ici, va à l'\c[3]ouest\c[0], près de la sortie.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: From there, you can make a jump to a higher platform to the \c[3]south\c[0].
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Là-bas, tu peux faire un saut sur une plateforme plus haute vers le \c[3]sud\c[0].

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: From there go all the way \c[3]south\c[0] until you reach the previous area.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: À partir de là, va tout au \c[3]sud\c[0] jusqu'à ce que tu atteignes l'endroit précédent.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: And from there...\. well...\. Actually there is quite a bit more and I can't remember it in detail.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Et de là...\. euh...\. il faut en faire un peu plus et je me souviens plus des détails.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Anyway, I'm sure you'll find the way. Just give it your best shot.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: En tout cas, je suis sûr que tu trouveras le chemin. Essaye juste de faire de ton mieux.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: [shakes head]
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: That's the spirit.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: C'est le bon état d'esprit.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: [yes]

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: [non]

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: So maybe now I can enjoy a quiet moment here.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Peut-être que maintenant je vais pouvoir profiter d'un petit moment de repos.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: It's okay. I can't refuse a fellow traveler in need.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: C'est bon. Je ne peux pas laisser tomber un confrère voyageur dans le besoin.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: [shakes head]
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: So you think you can manage on your own?
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Donc tu penses que tu y arriveras toute seule ?

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.orig: Good luck, then.
maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: Bonne chance, alors.

maps/autumn/path-7-2.json/entities/741/s.text: [oui]
